<p>&amp; got 50 Germans in both.<br/>To night we got our new pay books they are a complicated affair.<br/>Jock Mackie has been pretty crook since yesterday &amp; tonight he is not much better.<br/>24th  Out on the same job again this morning, but they might as well stop home for all the work they do<br/>This morning Bell &amp; I went away for a little while &amp; when we came back there was nothing but a long row of picks &amp; shovels leaning against the roadside "what a pretty sight"  I wonder what the officer would have said if he had seen them, it was disgraceful  they were all away looking for canteens &amp; etc it would take a good man to find a</p>
